	(1, 1, 'Mr WordPress', '', 'http://wordpress.org/', '', '2011-03-15 20:00:10', '2011-03-15 20:00:10', 'Hi, this is a comment.<br />To delete a comment, just log in and view the post&#039;s comments. There you will have the option to edit or delete them.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
	(2, 11, 'Son nH', 'huysondt@gmail.com', 'http://creativevoi.com', '127.0.0.1', '2012-02-17 03:10:38', '2012-02-17 03:10:38', 'Testing comment\r\nAnd another test <a href="http://google.com" rel="nofollow">here</a>\r\n\r\nGood point!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 5.1; rv:10.0.1) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/10.0.1', '', 0, 0),
	(4, 11, 'Son nH', 'huysondt@gmail.com', 'http://creativevoi.com', '127.0.0.1', '2012-02-17 03:49:19', '2012-02-17 03:49:19', 'We want to keep improving the Will Kit.\r\nSo, please leave your comments, we\'d really appreciate it.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 5.1; rv:10.0.1) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/10.0.1', '', 2, 0),
	(5, 11, 'Son nH', 'huysondt@gmail.com', 'http://creativevoi.com', '127.0.0.1', '2012-02-17 03:50:16', '2012-02-17 03:50:16', 'Quisque tristique consequat accumsan. Mauris vel neque nunc. Duis sapien nunc, dictum ac viverra quis, elementum sed dui. Fusce facilisis tincidunt risus vel rutrum. Nulla vehicula justo quis metus semper hendrerit a sed leo. Mauris volutpat sodales dolor non dapibus. Etiam quis mi nec mi tempor sollicitudin vitae sed leo. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Aenean ipsum tortor, iaculis ac mattis aliquet, tristique non mauris. Cras eu augue sem, nec volutpat nibh. Nulla facilisi. Phasellus sem urna, auctor vel eleifend sit amet, faucibus vel enim. Suspendisse et quam id nibh sollicitudin varius. Curabitur porta leo sed massa sollicitudin vel adipiscing justo tincidunt.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 5.1; rv:10.0.1) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/10.0.1', '', 0, 0),
	(6, 11, 'Son nH', 'huysondt@gmail.com', 'http://creativevoi.com', '127.0.0.1', '2012-02-17 03:54:53', '2012-02-17 03:54:53', 'There’s offen a lot of confusion out there in relation to “what actually is a will”.\r\n\r\nPeople sometimes confuse a Will with a Power of Attorney. Well, they’re completely different.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 5.1; rv:10.0.1) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/10.0.1', '', 4, 0),
	(7, 11, 'admin', 'creativevoi@gmail.com', '', '127.0.0.1', '2012-02-17 03:58:49', '2012-02-17 03:58:49', 'asdasdasd', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 5.1; rv:10.0.1) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/10.0.1', '', 0, 1);
